long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Track your mood and journal your thoughts right in your browser!

Growth Tracker features:
    >Daily mood tracking
    >Daily Journaling
    >Year overview
    >View and edit past entries
    >Export mood/journal history

    >Calming plant theme
